	r purchase. ADA tickets can be purchased online - you do not need to call 
	the box office to place an order. Look for the logo on the Find Tickets pa
	ge to view all available accessible seats. We do have accessible seating i
	n every price range but be advised it may sell out. We have very limited s
	eating available for guests on the day of the event so please make sure yo
	u purchase accessible seating when you order tickets. Bags up to 12" x 6" 
